{"tid":1381690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地應該善用人多勢眾既威力","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:40:07.000Z","uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc34d9814a0fcb9e00d8dd120ed316fe5b4a4bab","tid":1381690,"uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"呢個威力唔係講緊同d著住制服/上晒裝既POPO硬碰。佢著住套野，你行過撞到佢都可以告你襲警，但當佢除左套衫/收左工，自然唔再有呢d任佢作既大話當成罪名黎保護佢。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該整返個綜合post/tg資訊group去cap低所有濫權、使用過份武力既黑警樣俾大家留底，全港十八區都有良好市民，點都有人認得佢啦，又或者有良心警察可以報料，到人人都認得佢，咁佢除左制服同面罩頭盔既時候就只係一隻過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚：<br />\n元朗凶人抄牌狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzBx6qp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzBx6qp.png&h=7518ee18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53c815942ffaef0bdcae048d0fa50eeb071ff0e9","tid":1381690,"uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d11edc4104bdf1967fcbb6e91484da0c9ae64c","tid":1381690,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 實行真係有難度, 加上之前小刮男單野告人襲警 風險幾高</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BiLuFcS90NLYcDmgy